Package: StatMonitor
Title: Interactive Biodiversity Monitoring Platform
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Manuel", "Spínola", 
           email = "manuel.spinola@una.ac.cr",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: A Shiny-based interactive platform for biodiversity monitoring,
    part of the StatSuite ecosystem. Includes modules for monitoring concepts,
    data loading, trend analysis, and analytical techniques. Designed for
    teaching and research in ecology and biodiversity sciences.
